{
  "name": "RPlog_Luke_and_Jessalyn",
  "title": "Luke and Jessalyn",
  "summary": "Aboard the YT-1300 Black Dragon, a frustrated Luke Skywalker confronts the injured Jessalyn Valios for following him into danger after he expressly told her not to come. Their argument lays bare a mutual, fearful protectiveness, she insisting she could not bear to watch him go off alone, he insisting she is not expendable and that he expected better of her. The tension dissolves into teasing banter and laughter as old warmth resurfaces, Luke threatening to jettison her as ballast and ribbing her about being Corellian. A playful tussle ends with Luke catching Jessalyn off balance, and in the close moment he impulsively kisses her, which she returns eagerly before both pull back flustered and embarrassed. Awkward and blushing, they agree they should get back to work, the unspoken shift in their relationship left hanging as Luke gathers his cloak and heads for the ramp.",
